Since revision 378 and for better maintenance of code 
and usage of sources, you just need to get this directory.
Originals Freeciv sources are given separatelly from 
warclient hacking.

To cleany merge freeciv-2.0.9 and warclient, just run :

chmod u+x ./run.sh
./run.sh <your_merged_dir>

Warning : if <your_merged_dir> is empty, default is set as "./merged/"

Follow instructions given in the output of ./run.sh
